# No Fake Proof Rule

**Strict Rule:** Do not invent or generate fake proof elements under any circumstances.

This includes:
- Fake testimonials
- Fake logos
- Fake ratings
- Fake reviews
- Fake revenue claims
- Fake compliance claims
- Fake guarantees
- Fake user counts
- Fake partner names
- Fake screenshots or UI output

Use evidence-based language only. If a claim cannot be proven from repo content or user-provided source material, do not include it.
